Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(277,472)\fnArial\fs11\c&H3B403A&\frz4.371\fax-0.25\pos(120.5,145.5)}{Views: 1,012}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(277,472)\an4\fnArial\fs12\c&H474E49&\fax-0.24\bord3\3c&HFDFFFD&\frz3.908\pos(65.5,217)}{Sorry I can't upload very often nowadays!\NThere's just so much going on at high school!\NNext time I'll try a song I do all the time\Nwith my friends at karaoke!}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:18.30,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(277,472)\an4\fnArial\fs11\c&H9DA09D&\fax-0.24\frz2.074\pos(45.5,305)}{10 comments                                      Sort}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{M-Me?!}M-Mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:15.56,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'll send you a link if you haven't!}Không biết thì tí tớ gửi link cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.16,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She's super awesome! You should hear her!}Cậu ta tuyệt lắm! Nghe thử đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Awe... some?}Tuyệt à...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.08,0:17:23.75,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{She comes up in my recommendations \Na lot, so I've seen her too.}Tớ cũng có nghe qua do nằm trong danh sách giới thiệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:25.14,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{She really is excellent.}Nhưng đúng là tuyệt thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Right?!}Còn gì nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.94,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Though her naming sense is a bit cringy...}Cơ mà cách đặt tên có hơi thốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It is?!}Thốn?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:33.52,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I follow her with notifications on!}Tớ đã đăng kí theo dõi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:35.78,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I'd love to play with her some day!}Ước gì ngày nào đó được diễn cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{You just did, actually...}Chị vừa diễn cùng rồi đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:41.28,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Look, what I'm getting at here}Tóm lại là...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.77,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{is that even awesome, popular people \Nare out there playing guitar,}ngoài kia vẫn còn nhiều người chơi ghita tuyệt vời,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.58,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{lots and lots of them,\Nin places we're not even watching.}Rất nhiều người mà chúng ta vẫn chưa biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You should watch her later!}Tí nữa em xem thử cậu ấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.95,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{ think you'll get what I mean\Nif you watch the videos.}Xem xong chị nghĩ em sẽ hiểu thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.65,0:18:00.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I always figured real-life people \Ndidn't care about me at all...}Mình nghĩ không ai ở thế giới thực quan tâm đến mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:05.94,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{You can't give up on playing in a band \Njust because it didn't work out today!}Đừng chỉ vì hôm nay mà \Ntừ bỏ ý định thành lập ban nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:08.29,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's possible it's our problem, anyway...}Tuy bọn chị cũng đang trên bờ vực tan rã nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.00,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Our problem?}Bọn mình á?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.09,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:14.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But someone this nice has been \Nwatching me all this time,}Nhưng vẫn có những người tốt bụng luôn quan sát mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and actually spoke to me...}Và bắt chuyện với mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:18.24,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{She stood up.}Đứng lên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:22.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's the kind of miracle \Nmost people never experience!}Kì tích này sẽ không xảy đến lần 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I can't let it go to waste!}Không thể bỏ phí.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.50,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I... I'm...}Em... Em...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.92,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{D-Do you want to perform after all?}Em muốn trình diễn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:34.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,Mình biết hết mọi thứ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:37.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{But I'm still too scared...}Nhưng vẫn sợ quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{There's no way I can play \Nin front of an audience...}Không thể nào đứng trước khán giả chơi được...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.33,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{If you're scared, \Nyou could play from in here.}Nếu sợ thì đội cái này vào nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:44.31,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(315,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\b1\c&H4144D1&\3c&HA5C1F0&\bord2\fax-0.05\frz3.591\pos(186,291)}{Ripe Mangos}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs36\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2.5\pos(328,198.5)}{Ripe Mangos}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:48.56,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I-It's the same environment \Nthat I play in all the time!}Y như nơi mọi ngày em luyện tập!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.19,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Where exactly do you live?}Em sống ở đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:56.15,Signs,sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\b1\c&H3844BE&\3c&HD1DEE8&\bord2\pos(330,51.5)}{Ripe Mangos}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.64,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{How you feelin' tonight, Shimo-Kita?!}Hôm nay hãy cháy lên nào, Shimokita!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.15,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{She's suddenly more outgoing.}Tự nhiên thay đổi hoàn toàn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:59.48,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{By the way, how do you \Nwant us to introduce you?}Cơ mà em muốn chị giới thiệu là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.17,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{"Hitori-chan"? Should we use your real name?}Hitori-chan? Dùng tên thật luôn hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.17,0:19:03.90,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'd... I'd rather not...}E-Em không nghĩ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.77,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Any nicknames, then?}Thế biệt danh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.02,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{In middle school, they called me \N"Hey" and "You there"...}Ở cấp 2 mọi người hay gọi em là "Ê" hay "Này"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:10.84,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{I don't think those are nicknames!}Cái đó không phải biệt danh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:14.79,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I never knew anyone well enough \Nto get nicknames from them!}Em chưa từng nghĩ phải có biệt danh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.22,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hitori...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.94,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hitoribocchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.94,0:19:19.12,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{How about Bocchi-chan?}Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.18,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Another tactless comment!}Nghe nặng nề quá vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.29,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm B-B-Bocchi!}E-Em là Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.14,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{She likes it?}Thích nó sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.18,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{It's just my first ever nickname...}Lần đầu em có biệt danh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:28.36,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{This is making me teary-eyed.}Tự nhiên thấy thương xót quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:31.03,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Oh, you haven't told me your band name yet.}A, em vẫn chưa biết tên ban nhạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.63,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It's Kessoku Band.}Là nhóm Kessoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.02,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Kessoku Band...}Kessoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:40.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Isn't that the word for "zip tie"?}Ủa? Là cái zip hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:42.57,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It's brilliant.}Zip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:44.82,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{It's the worst pun! \NWe're totally changing it!}Quá tệ! Phải đổi tên ngay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.60,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Why? It's cute.}Tại sao? Dễ thương mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.81,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Y-Yes.}V-Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:52.05,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Band name aside, it's time to play!}Bỏ cái tên đi, giờ là lúc diễn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.42,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:58.55,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{The key is to have fun, even if you suck!}Chỉ cần vui vẻ tận hưởng thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Your feelings really come \Nout in your playing, see?}Cảm xúc sẽ tuôn trào khi em chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.68,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{R-Right...}V-Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:07.04,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We can always work on the \Nskill part next time.}Chúng ta có thể luyện tập kĩ năng sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:07.72,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.13,0:20:09.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Next... time...}Lần sau...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.78,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay, let's go!}Rồi, đi nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:11.38,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Right.}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:15.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{They're okay with there being a next time!}Bọn họ muốn chơi cùng mình nữa sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.24,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you! We're Kessoku Band!}Rất vui được gặp! Nhóm Kessoku đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:25.26,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{We'll play a bunch of \Nsongs you probably know,}Hôm nay cả nhóm sẽ chơi những bài hát nổi tiếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:26.32,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{so please enjoy!}Nên hãy vui vẻ nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:27.70,Default,Seika,0,0,0,,{Who's that?}Ai kia?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:41.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I hate that I can't play as \Nwell as I usually do, but...}Mình ghét việc không thể chơi như mọi khi nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:46.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{playing in a band with other \Npeople is so much fun!}chơi cùng mọi người trong ban nhạc thật vui.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I've never really shone before today...}Hôm nay là ngày mình toả sáng nhất...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{And I still don't!}Làm gì có!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:57.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{This might actually be a low point for me!}Ngược lại là ngày thảm hại nhất!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:02.88,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Boy, I screwed up!}Thoải mái quá đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:04.80,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Your intro bombed, too.}Phần giới thiệu bị trật nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.82,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{E-Excuse me!}X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:07.53,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-B-B...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.39,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.39,0:21:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{B-B-B-B-B...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:11.73,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay, you're freaking me out!}Đáng sợ quá đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:17.01,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{B-Before our next performance, I'm gonna get \Nbrave enough to say hello to my classmates!}Lần diễn tới em sẽ cố gắng chào hỏi mọi người trong lớp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.17,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{What a dramatic declaration.}Tuyên ngôn nghe đáng thương vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:20.25,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Such growth...}Trưởng thành rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.60,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Okay, I get it.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.32,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Sure!}Ừm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:26.55,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{Then let's have a Bocchi-chan-welcome-party-\Nslash-concert-post-mortem!}Vậy thì mở tiệc chào mừng Bocchi lần đầu diễn live nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:30.26,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Actually, I'm pretty exhausted from \Nall this social interaction, so I'm gonna go.}Thực ra hôm nay em khá kiệt sức nên xin phép về.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.63,0:21:31.85,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I'm sleepy.}Tớ buồn ngủ quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.28,0:21:33.76,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{P-Pardon me!}Em xin phép!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:41.22,Default,Nijika,0,0,0,,{There's no "ties" in this band at all!}Chẳng có cái liên kết nào ở cái ban nhạc này vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna get over my social anxiety}Mình sẽ chữa bệnh anti xã hội
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.30,0:21:54.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and bring out my full guitarhero powers!}và đưa sức mạnh của ghitahero ra ánh sáng!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.89,0:21:57.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{For Nijika-chan,}Nijika-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{Ryo-san,}Ryo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.25,0:22:01.21,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0,0,0,,{and Kessoku Band!}và ban nhạc Kessoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:04.96,Default,Hitori,0,0,0,,{S-Sorry! Sorry!}X-Xin lỗi!
